<div id="review_1672754982" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1672754982" />
    <a title="BookAddict  ✒ La Crimson Femme" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme"><img alt="BookAddict  ✒ La Crimson Femme" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1537761015p2/3089655.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1672754982?book_show_action=true">Jun 18, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="BookAddict  ✒ La Crimson Femme" class="user" itemprop="url" name="BookAddict  ✒ La Crimson Femme" href="/user/show/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme">BookAddict  ✒ La Crimson Femme</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme?shelf=paranormal-romance">paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme?shelf=vampire">vampire</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3089655-bookaddict-la-crimson-femme?shelf=borrowed-kindle">borrowed-kindle</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1672754982" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15311708185724426785">This is a surprise sleeper story for me. I&apos;ve read Ms. Schroeder once before and she was enjoyable but not too memorable. This one is definitely memorable. It is rare for me to come across a vampire story set in historical London. I liked the premise. The world building was decent. I hoped for more and expect to learn more in the following books. The characters were stereotypical arrogant male and bluestocking female. I liked this about the historical paranormal romance. <br/><br/>The sex in this story is</span>
  <span id="freeText15311708185724426785" style="display:none">This is a surprise sleeper story for me. I've read Ms. Schroeder once before and she was enjoyable but not too memorable. This one is definitely memorable. It is rare for me to come across a vampire story set in historical London. I liked the premise. The world building was decent. I hoped for more and expect to learn more in the following books. The characters were stereotypical arrogant male and bluestocking female. I liked this about the historical paranormal romance. <br /><br />The sex in this story is reminiscent of bodice rippers. Good for those who enjoy sweet erotica. For those who enjoy kinky sex, this is a bit too tame. I whipped through the sex scenes as they were a bit too boring for me. The rest of the story moves at a decent pace and resolutions are not unexpected. The ending is sweet and teases the reader into looking for the next book in the series. </span>
  <a data-text-id="15311708185724426785" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


