        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer423724346" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3613984758076502812">Desire by Blood (By Blood, #1) is one damn sexy vampire romance. In Desire by Blood Melissa Schroeder really made you feel connected to a wide variety of characters. Each of them with a distinct story and personality. Although the main plot was centered around Cordelia Collingsworth and Nicodemus Blackburn, many of those secondary characters were clearly memorable. Desire by Blood has a strong historical feel. Melissa Schroeder then spun into this historical setting some very strong alpha vampir</span>
  <span id="freeText3613984758076502812" style="display:none">Desire by Blood (By Blood, #1) is one damn sexy vampire romance. In Desire by Blood Melissa Schroeder really made you feel connected to a wide variety of characters. Each of them with a distinct story and personality. Although the main plot was centered around Cordelia Collingsworth and Nicodemus Blackburn, many of those secondary characters were clearly memorable. Desire by Blood has a strong historical feel. Melissa Schroeder then spun into this historical setting some very strong alpha vampires who are following a different set of rules. Women are valued, protected, and respected, and in the case of Nico’s mother – feared. Melissa Schroeder made you feel like part of the family. Cordelia was fantastic. She was quick witted, feisty, and passionate. The passion between Nico and Cordelia was smokin’ hot, steamy, and unforgettable. Melissa Schroeder writing is flawless. Seriously. The sexual tension and scenes fit perfectly into a wonderful and complete story that I will not soon forget.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3613984758076502812" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

