  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/434975075" />
    <a title="The Smutty Kitty" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4351423-the-smutty-kitty"><img alt="The Smutty Kitty" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1371079762p2/4351423.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/434975075?book_show_action=true">Oct 15, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="The Smutty Kitty" class="user" itemprop="url" name="The Smutty Kitty" href="/user/show/4351423-the-smutty-kitty">The Smutty Kitty</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer434975075" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10753721732477392360">As posted on The Smutty Kitty<br/><br/>5 out of 5 Licks<br/><br/>I LOVE finding books that I can’t put down and Desire By Blood was definitely one of them!! I finally had to force myself to turn off my K Fire last night while I was reading because the words got all blurry. lol I’m having a hard time finding the words to describe how much I enjoyed this book, but I’ll try. The story just sucked me in. There are murders, hot sex, romance, and did I mention the hot sex? I don’t know that I would call myself a big hist</span>
  <span id="freeText10753721732477392360" style="display:none">As posted on The Smutty Kitty<br /><br />5 out of 5 Licks<br /><br />I LOVE finding books that I can’t put down and Desire By Blood was definitely one of them!! I finally had to force myself to turn off my K Fire last night while I was reading because the words got all blurry. lol I’m having a hard time finding the words to describe how much I enjoyed this book, but I’ll try. The story just sucked me in. There are murders, hot sex, romance, and did I mention the hot sex? I don’t know that I would call myself a big historical fan but adding the vampires into the mix really does it for me. Who doesn’t like a sexy vamp? No one that’s who! ;) Nico is a strong, stubborn man (just the way I like them) and Cordelia is a strong, stubborn woman. I always enjoy a heroine who will kick her man’s ass! All too often I read about wimpy women who don’t know their own worth and the man eats them alive. Cordelia may not think she is a knockout but thanks to her horrid past she is strong and more than willing to give Nico a verbal thrashing a time or two.<br /> <br />You know I don’t like to give any spoilers but all I can say is I can’t wait for more in this series. I want at least 4 more books and I would love to read Nico’s mother and father’s story too. lol I’m a sucker for a series. So run, don’t walk, to your computer and snatch this one up now!! You won’t regret it!</span>
  <a data-text-id="10753721732477392360" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


