<div id="review_749632828" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/749632828" />
    <a title="Netanella" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1157679-netanella"><img alt="Netanella" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1226895280p2/1157679.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/749632828?book_show_action=true">Oct 25, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Netanella" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Netanella" href="/user/show/1157679-netanella">Netanella</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1157679-netanella?shelf=historical-romance">historical-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1157679-netanella?shelf=vampires">vampires</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1157679-netanella?shelf=victorian">victorian</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1157679-netanella?shelf=2014-may-reading-challenges">2014-may-reading-challenges</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer749632828" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2515230473708039833">A well-done blend of historical romance set in the Victorian era and paranormal romance of a secret alliance of vampires who move easily within the glittering balls of upper class. The author does a impressive job in combining the romantic elements of the story with a fairly unique vampire mythos.<br/><br/>Beyond the petticoats and bonnets and cravats is a society of vampires, living amongst the humans for hundreds of years. And just like their mortal counterparts, the vampires too have their social caste</span>
  <span id="freeText2515230473708039833" style="display:none">A well-done blend of historical romance set in the Victorian era and paranormal romance of a secret alliance of vampires who move easily within the glittering balls of upper class. The author does a impressive job in combining the romantic elements of the story with a fairly unique vampire mythos.<br /><br />Beyond the petticoats and bonnets and cravats is a society of vampires, living amongst the humans for hundreds of years. And just like their mortal counterparts, the vampires too have their social caste system, dividing themselves into the elitist Borns and the lower Mades. Add to this mix a human female bloodline of Carriers who are capable of birthing little vampy babies, and you get an interesting set up for a wonderfully told story. <br /><br />Recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2515230473708039833" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


