        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2514170647" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer714216004866936860">This is a Victorian Paranormal Romance. I like vampire books, but Melissa Schroeder’s vampire world is different than most others I had read. I really enjoyed the differences. The characters are both determined characters and when they get together it is explosive. The pace of the story is great and the characters are well developed. This is a great paranormal romance.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


