        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer365087465" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8148375023618216173">Nico is HAWTness!!! <br/><br/>Not all authors can mix Paranormal and Victorian romance, but Melissa Schroeder does just that and makes you want more! <br/>Nicodemus &quot;Nico&quot; Blackburn is out to protect the vampire world from all that can go wrong and the humans that don&apos;t suspect that they exist. And within this world, he is still trying to decide if love is in his cards. He is known to be one of the most eligible bachelors and this keeps people wondering about him. <br/>Lady Cordelia Collingsworth is not what they c</span>
  <span id="freeText8148375023618216173" style="display:none">Nico is HAWTness!!! <br /><br />Not all authors can mix Paranormal and Victorian romance, but Melissa Schroeder does just that and makes you want more! <br />Nicodemus "Nico" Blackburn is out to protect the vampire world from all that can go wrong and the humans that don't suspect that they exist. And within this world, he is still trying to decide if love is in his cards. He is known to be one of the most eligible bachelors and this keeps people wondering about him. <br />Lady Cordelia Collingsworth is not what they considered normal and prestigious. She was born into circumstances that kept her from being fully accepted. But this only made her fight harder for a life that was her own. So when she runs into Nico, she is determined to find out his REAL story. Unfortunately, looking for this story started a series of events that both Nico and Cordelia weren't prepared for. <br />Nico &amp; Cordelia have a lot to learn about each other and they don't have that much time to do it before they are forced to live by societies rules. <br />This story draws you in... Whether you are a fan of paranormal creatures/vampires or maybe historical/Victorian era or just all things romance, you will be drawn into the world that has been created and the twists &amp; turns that the characters are often forced to take. <br />There are supporting characters that you want to know more about and you will definitely keep wanting to know more about who keeps causing so much trouble. <br />I can't wait to see what more comes from this series! Nicodemus Blackburn will be a hard one to top! <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="8148375023618216173" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
